'''2015年巴马科丽笙酒店袭击事件'''是指2015年11月20日在[[马里|马里]]首都及其最大城市[[巴马科|巴马科]][[丽笙酒店|丽笙酒店]]发生的袭击事件<ref name="cnn._Gunm">{{cite news| title = Gunmen take hostages at Radisson Blu hotel in Mali| work = CNN| date = 2015-11-20| accessdate = 2015-11-20| url = http://www.cnn.com/2015/11/20/africa/mali-shooting/| archive-date = 2019-05-01| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190501172450/https://www.cnn.com/2015/11/20/africa/mali-shooting/| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="NYTSearcey">Dionne Searcey & Adam Nossiternov, [http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/21/world/africa/mali-hotel-attack-radisson.html Mali Hotel Attack Leaves Dozens Dead; Hostages Are Taken] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/21/world/africa/mali-hotel-attack-radisson.html |date=20180129015059 }},纽约时报(20 November 2015).</ref>。在[[特种部队|特种部队]]突击进入酒店并释放幸存的人质前<ref name="No more">[http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-34879955# Mali hotel attack: 'No more hostages' after special forces raid] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-34879955 |date=20170622051553 }}, BBC News, 20 November 2015</ref><ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-34877069|title = Mali attack: Special forces storm hotel to free hostages|date = 2015-11-20|website = BBC News|accessdate = 2015-11-21|archive-date = 2019-03-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190329164246/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-34877069|dead-url = no}}</ref>，事件共导致19人死亡，大部分是外籍人士<ref name="Reuters">{{cite news|author=Tiemoko Diallo|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/11/20/us-mali-attacks-idUSKCN0T90SK20151120|title=At least 27 dead after Islamists seize luxury hotel in Mali's capital|work=Reuters|date=2015-11-20|accessdate=2015-11-21|archive-date=2015-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123033534/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/11/20/us-mali-attacks-iduskcn0t90sk20151120|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隶属于[[基地组织|基地组织]]的非洲极端团体{{link-en|西非圣战统一运动|Al-Mourabitoun}}在其Twitter上宣称，此次袭击是他们所为，但尚未被证实<ref name="Reuters"/><ref name="马里人质事件落幕 至少有27人死亡">{{cite news|url=http://cn.rfi.fr/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2/20151121-%E9%A9%AC%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%B4%A8%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E8%90%BD%E5%B9%95-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E6%9C%8927%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1|title=马里人质事件落幕 至少有27人死亡|work=法广|date=2015年11月21日|accessdate=2015年11月21日|archive-date=2016年3月4日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304120849/http://cn.rfi.fr/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2/20151121-%E9%A9%AC%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%B4%A8%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E8%90%BD%E5%B9%95-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E6%9C%8927%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景==
此次事件的事发酒店巴马科[[丽笙酒店|丽笙酒店]]，是当地最好最安全的豪华酒店，也是外国商人和政府官员经常下榻的地方，位于使馆区附近，酒店有190个房间，通常有九成左右入住率。该酒店隶属于总部位于美国的[[卡尔森瑞德酒店集团|卡尔森瑞德酒店集团]]<ref>{{cite web|title = Where is Bamako and why has the Radisson hotel been targeted by terrorists?|url = http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/mali-hotel-siege-bamako-radisson-6866044|website = The Daily Mirror|publisher = Trinity Mirror plc|accessdate = 2015-11-20|date = 2015-11-20|last = Dubuis|first = Anna|archive-date = 2018-12-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181211132204/https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/mali-hotel-siege-bamako-radisson-6866044|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="震动世界"/>。

==经过==
2015年11月20日上午7:00-7:30之间，有四至五名枪手到达巴马科丽笙酒店。根据酒店工作人员的供述，这些男子当时驾驶着挂有外交车牌的车辆前往酒店<ref name="NYTSearcey"/>。据安全部门消息人士和马里陆军司令称，约有10名枪手进入酒店，在他们开枪射击时高喊“[[大赞辞|真主至大]]”的口号<ref name=WP>{{cite news|last1=Kaplan|first1=Sarah|last2=Murphy|first2=Brian|title=Gunmen attack luxury hotel in Mali capital, take 170 hostages|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/11/20/reports-gunmen-attack-luxury-hotel-in-mali-capital-take-hostages/?hpid=hp_hp-top-table-high_mm-mali-410am%3Ahomepage%2Fstory|accessdate=2015-11-20|agency=The Washington Post|date=2015-11-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.sohu.com/20151120/n427361725.shtml|title=消息称马里参加袭击枪手开枪高喊“真主伟大”|work=财经网|date=2015年11月20日|accessdate=2015年11月21日|archive-date=2015年11月21日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121223133/http://news.sohu.com/20151120/n427361725.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一名被获救的人质，几内亚歌手塞古巴·“班比诺”·迪亚巴特表示，当时在酒店停留，事发后便逃离<ref name=BBCNov20>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/world-africa-34815762|title=Africa Live: Shooting at hotel in Mali's capital|work=BBC News Online|accessdate=2015-11-20|archive-date=2015-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120095517/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/world-africa-34815762|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另据报道，枪手之间用英语交流<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newindianexpress.com/world/At-Least-27-Dead-in-Mali-Hotel-Attack-Claimed-by-Al-Qaeda-Affiliate/2015/11/21/article3139540.ece|title=At Least 27 Dead in Mali Hotel Attack Claimed by Al-Qaeda Affiliate|work=The New Indian Express|accessdate=2015-11-21|archive-date=2015-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121150743/http://www.newindianexpress.com/world/At-Least-27-Dead-in-Mali-Hotel-Attack-Claimed-by-Al-Qaeda-Affiliate/2015/11/21/article3139540.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这些枪手将酒店中140多名游客和30名酒店工作人员，共170多人劫为人质，并将其扣押<ref>{{cite news|title='No more hostages' as Mali hotel stormed|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/11/gunmen-hostages-mali-hotel-reports-151120084719883.html|accessdate=2015-11-20|agency=Aljazeera|publisher=Al Jazeera and agencies|date=2015-11-20|archive-date=2015-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120101107/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/11/gunmen-hostages-mali-hotel-reports-151120084719883.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="震动世界">{{cite news|url=http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2015-11/8020554.html|title=马里逾百人质经历惊魂一天 恐怖的一周震动世界|work=环球时报|date=2015年11月21日|accessdate=2015年11月21日|archive-date=2015年11月21日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121170029/http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2015-11/8020554.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当时，[[法语圈国际组织|法语圈国际组织]]代表团在酒店停留<ref name="NYTSearcey"/>。

据报道称，被劫持的人质中包括10名中国公民、20名印度公民、约10余名美国公民（包括来自美国驻马里大使馆的人员），7名阿尔及利亚公民（包括6名外交官）、2名俄罗斯公民、2名摩洛哥公民，7名[[土耳其航空公司|土耳其航空公司]]的工作人员、以及法国公民（具体人数不详，包括1名法籍华人）<ref name=BBCNov20/><ref name=TimeofIndiaNov20>{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/Islamist-gunmen-attack-luxury-hotel-in-Mali-capital/liveblog/49859711.cms|title=Live Blog: Islamist gunmen attack luxury hotel in Mali capital|work=Times of India|date=2015-11-20|accessdate=2015-11-20|archive-date=2015-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120143549/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/Islamist-gunmen-attack-luxury-hotel-in-Mali-capital/liveblog/49859711.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外12名[[法国航空|法国航空]]机组人员亦在酒店停留，后安全撤离<ref name=":0">{{cite web|title = World News liveblog|url = http://live.reuters.com/Event/World_News?ShowComments=0|website = Reuters|accessdate = 2015-11-20|archive-date = 2015-11-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151120203918/http://live.reuters.com/Event/World_News?ShowComments=0|dead-url = no}}</ref>；而一些联合国的官员也安全撤离了酒店<ref>{{cite news|title = Gunmen take hostages at Radisson Blu hotel in Bamako|url = http://www.cnn.com/2015/11/20/africa/mali-shooting/index.html|website = CNN|accessdate = 2015-11-20|archive-date = 2015-11-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151120115704/http://www.cnn.com/2015/11/20/africa/mali-shooting/index.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。在被劫持的人质中，有超过100名人质被获救并释放<ref>{{cite web|title = Mali hotel attack leaves at least 27 dead after 170 taken hostage|url = http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-11-20/mali-hotel-attack-leaves-dozens-dead/6960442|website = ABC News|accessdate = 2015-11-20}}</ref>。

槍手要求人質背誦[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]的[[清真言|清真言]]，以分辨該人是否[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]，如果是穆斯林就獲准離開酒店<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/21/world/africa/mali-hotel-attack-radisson.html |title=Deadly Siege Ends After Assault on Hotel in Mali |publisher=The New York Times |date=2015-11-20 |accessdate=2015-11-21 |archive-date=2018-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180129015059/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/21/world/africa/mali-hotel-attack-radisson.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

事发后，马里警察和军队赶到现场，包围酒店并发起解救行动，以保障酒店及周边安全。驻马里的法国军队和[[联合国维和部队|联合国维和部队]]人员也到场<ref name="BBCNov20" /><ref name="被劫">{{cite news|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20151121/46332075_0.shtml|title=马里人质事件：酒店已无人质被劫|work=新华网|date=2015年11月21日|accessdate=2015年11月21日|archive-date=2015年11月22日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122021747/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20151121/46332075_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而一批驻马里的美国特种部队士兵将“帮助把平民（人质）转移到安全地点”，包括至少6名美国公民<ref name="被劫"/>。

===死者===
据联合国的统计数字，[[联合国维和部队|联合国维和部队]]人员在酒店内发现27具尸体；而根据马里总统办公室的统计，有20人死于此次枪击事件<ref name="Reuters"/>。这20名死者包括6名马里平民、1名比利时[[瓦隆大区|瓦隆]]议会官员<ref name="Reuters"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/11/20/africa/mali-shooting/|title=Mali hotel attack: Gunmen take hostages at Radisson Blu in Bamako - CNN.com|author=Ed Payne and Jason Hanna, CNN|date=2015-11-20|work=CNN|accessdate=2015-11-21|archive-date=2019-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190125044400/https://edition.cnn.com/2015/11/20/africa/mali-shooting/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/france/12006988/Mali-Bamako-terrorist-attack-170-hostages-Paris-live.html|title=Mali hotel attack: 27 dead with no more hostages held at Radisson Blu as third body found at Paris terrorist lair – live|publisher=telegraph.co.uk|date=2015-11-20|accessdate=2015-11-20|archive-date=2015-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121071851/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/france/12006988/Mali-Bamako-terrorist-attack-170-hostages-Paris-live.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、1名美国公民<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.presstv.com/Detail/2015/11/20/438497/US-Mali-terrorist-attack-Radisson-Blu-hotel|title=PressTV|work=presstv.com|accessdate=2015-11-21|archive-date=2015-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121234053/http://presstv.com/Detail/2015/11/20/438497/US-Mali-terrorist-attack-Radisson-Blu-hotel|dead-url=no}}</ref>及3名中国公民，这3名中国公民均为[[中国铁建|中国铁建]]下属中国铁建国际集团的高管<ref>{{cite news|url=http://finance.chinanews.com/gn/2015/11-21/7634720.shtml|title=中铁建证实3名高管在马里遇难 已部署善后处置工作|work=中国新闻网|date=2015年11月21日|accessdate=2015年11月21日|archive-date=2015年11月22日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122011610/http://finance.chinanews.com/gn/2015/11-21/7634720.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而6名俄罗斯人均为[[伏尔加-第聂伯航空|伏尔加-第聂伯航空]]的员工<ref>Diallo, Tiemoko and Adama Diarra. "[http://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/putin-seeks-global-anti-terrorism-fight-after-mali-attack/ar-BBnhwAL?li=BBnb7Kz&ocid=SK2FDHP Putin seeks global anti-terrorism fight after Mali attack] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6dEWi7bWe?url=http://www.msn.com/en-us/news/world/putin-seeks-global-anti-terrorism-fight-after-mali-attack/ar-BBnhwAL?li=BBnb7Kz |date=20151122161254 |dateformat=iso }}" (). [[Reuters|Reuters]].</ref>。

11月28日，此次事件中遇难的3名[[中国公民|中国公民]]的灵柩归国<ref>{{cite news|url=http://economy.gmw.cn/newspaper/2015-11/29/content_110009653.htm|title=回家　马里恐怖袭击遇难中国公民灵柩归国|work=中国新闻网|date=2015年11月29日|accessdate=2015年11月30日|archive-date=2015年12月8日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208062337/http://economy.gmw.cn/newspaper/2015-11/29/content_110009653.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

