==袭击策划者==
事后，隶属于[[基地组织|基地组织]]的非洲极端团体{{link-en|西非圣战统一运动|Al-Mourabitoun}}在其Twitter上宣称，此次袭击是他们所为，但尚未被证实<ref name="Reuters"/><ref name="Ilsley">{{cite web|author=Natalie Ilsley|url=http://www.newsweek.com/islamist-group-claims-responsibility-mali-attack-396659|title=Al-Mourabitoun Group Claims Responsibility for Mali Attack|work=Newsweek|date=2015-11-20|accessdate=2015-11-21|archive-date=2015-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151209030400/http://www.newsweek.com/islamist-group-claims-responsibility-mali-attack-396659|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据[[半岛电视台|半岛电视台]]所播出的录音，该组织已承诺与[[伊斯兰马格里布基地组织|伊斯兰马格里布基地组织]]进行联合攻击<ref name="Boshnaq">{{cite web|author=Mona Boshnaq|url=http://www.nytimes.com/live/mali-hotel-attack-latest-updates/al-mourabitoun-takes-responsibility-for-siege-al-jazeera-reports/|title=Al Mourabitoun Claims Responsibility for Mali Siege, Al Jazeera Reports|work=New York Times|date=2015-11-20|accessdate=2015-11-21|archive-date=2015-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121014636/http://www.nytimes.com/live/mali-hotel-attack-latest-updates/al-mourabitoun-takes-responsibility-for-siege-al-jazeera-reports/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

